eavesdropping being that door,

17:52.839 --> 17:54.306
it sounds like you need
a little more,

17:54.308 --> 17:56.575
uh...fake breasts.

17:56.577 --> 17:58.243
-No.
-Pure oxygen.

17:58.245 --> 17:59.378
I thought
you were the doctor.

17:59.380 --> 18:00.579
Well, you'll never know.

18:00.581 --> 18:03.382
Both:
And that's the fun part.

18:03.384 --> 18:04.983
Concealed.

18:04.985 --> 18:07.252
