19:57.964 --> 19:59.764
[ Laughter ]

19:59.766 --> 20:02.967
Oh-oh, yes.
I told you.

20:02.969 --> 20:06.104
When the feathers, dry,
we're in business.

20:06.106 --> 20:09.041
